Me and my SPF lip balms? Unstoppable 💄🛡️ 
While the world forgets lips need sunscreen too, I’m out here running a fully protected pout patrol 💋🌞

Let’s break down the gang:

1. @mycarmex Classic Stick & Pot (SPF 15)
🧊 The medicated legend. Heals, protects, and gives that icy tingle like a mini spa for your lips.
🪩 Pot = desk flex. Stick = bag essential.
🛠️ Always reliable, like your lip therapist in a tube.

2. Blistex Medicated Balm (SPF 15)
💨 Menthol magic. Instantly soothes chapped lips and makes them feel reborn.
Kind of like lip CPR.

3. @foxtaleskin Brightening Balm (SPF 30)
💄 Tinted, juicy, and secretly powerful. With Vitamin C, E & Hyaluronic Acid – it’s skincare dressed as lip balm.
💃 This is the “I woke up like this” balm.

4.  @dotandkey.skincare Gloss Boss (SPF 50)
🍉 Watermelon-cool. SPF 50 strong. Glossy finish.
✨ Basically sunscreen and lip gloss had a high-functioning child.

Lips are skin too — protect them like you mean it.
🚫 Burnt lips? No thanks.
🚫 Cracks and flakes? Hard pass.
✅ Hydrated, glossy, sun-safe lips? Always.

🌿✨ Superfood Secret for Gorgeous Indian Hair! ✨🌿
Want longer, stronger, shinier hair? Start with your breakfast bowl, not your shampoo! 💁🏽‍♀️⁣
⁣
💧 Soak 10–12 black raisins + 1 spoon pumpkin seeds overnight 🌙
👉 Eat them first thing in the morning = scalp love + hair goals unlocked 💫⁣
⁣
🖤 Black Raisins – Rich in iron & antioxidants, they boost blood flow to the scalp, reduce hair fall, and help prevent early greys.⁣
⁣
🎃 Pumpkin Seeds – Loaded with zinc, magnesium, and omega-3s. They support hair growth, strengthen roots, and keep your scalp balanced and happy.⁣
⁣
🌺 Why it’s amazing for Indian hair: Our hair often battles heat, sweat, and pollution. These soaked gems work from within to nourish each strand, naturally.⁣
⁣
✨ Quick tip: Keep it consistent – 21 days = noticeable difference 💪⁣
⁣

Because when life gives you mangoes, papaya & pom juice — you don’t ask questions. You GLOW.
☀️ + 🍉 + 🥭 = 💖

⸻

What’s on the glow menu today?

Fruit facial? Nah. Fruit FEAST:
- Papaya 🍑 = the ✨ enzyme queen ✨ for clear, acne-free skin
- Watermelon 🍉 = hydration station, 92% water & 100% glow
- Mango 🥭 = beta-carotene rich baddie for that sunkissed radiance
- Banana 🍌 = soft skin, happy gut, better mood — all in one bite
- Guava & Apple 🍏🍎 = vitamin C bomb for collagen + glow
- Muskmelon 🍈 = cools you down & calms the skin (and the drama)

That drink? Pomegranate juice, baby. ❤️
Packed with antioxidants, iron, and straight-up ✨ goddess juice ✨.
She clears your skin, boosts blood flow, and fights pigmentation — flawless behavior only.

⸻

Shivanii’s Summer Skin Rules (fun, not optional):
1. Snack pretty. 🍓 If it’s juicy, seasonal & colorful — it belongs in your bowl.
2. Sip smart. 🥤 Water, coconut water, pomegranate — keep it hydrating & healing.
3. Cut the fried fomo. 🍟 Your skin hates it more than your gut does.
4. Soak your almonds & flex those seeds. 🌰✨ Gut health = glow.
5. Fresh > fancy. 🧃 Homemade juice > overpriced bottled “wellness.”

⸻

Moral of the fruit salad:
You don’t need a 10-step skincare routine.
You just need a plate full of vitamins, a glass of glow, and a vibe.
